00:35:00.443 --> 00:35:03.260 align:middle line:90%
and I said, well, that was real.

00:35:03.260 --> 00:35:06.284 align:middle line:90%
You know, I felt it.

00:35:06.284 --> 00:35:10.117 align:middle line:84%
Now, I don't know if that
was my son's way of--

00:35:10.117 --> 00:35:11.700 align:middle line:84%
he likes to kid
around, and he knows I

00:35:11.700 --> 00:35:14.450 align:middle line:84%
like my hair in
proper place maybe.

00:35:14.450 --> 00:35:17.220 align:middle line:84%
I don't know, but I
definitely did feel something.

00:35:17.220 --> 00:35:23.310 align:middle line:84%
>> I had the definite sensation
that somebody came in from

00:35:23.310 --> 00:35:27.180 align:middle line:84%
behind the mirror around to
my left side and was just kind

00:35:27.180 --> 00:35:31.530 align:middle line:84%
of being there, and I wasn't
quite sure who it was or, you

00:35:31.530 --> 00:35:33.760 align:middle line:84%
know, if it was my
grandmother or not,

00:35:33.760 --> 00:35:36.840 align:middle line:84%
but a little while after
