00:35:38.790 --> 00:35:42.840 align:middle line:84%
So I felt that that
was the connection

00:35:42.840 --> 00:35:44.490 align:middle line:90%
that she had been there.

00:35:44.490 --> 00:35:47.870 align:middle line:90%
It was intuitive.

00:35:47.870 --> 00:35:50.010 align:middle line:84%
I was asking the
question internally,

00:35:50.010 --> 00:35:53.250 align:middle line:84%
