lot of different ways

00:36:01.530 --> 00:36:04.020 align:middle line:84%
to receive information,
a lot of people

00:36:04.020 --> 00:36:06.360 align:middle line:90%
experience information visually.

00:36:06.360 --> 00:36:09.600 align:middle line:84%
I've had oral or hearing
type of information.

00:36:09.600 --> 00:36:13.860 align:middle line:84%
I've smelled different
smells or scents, as well as

00:36:13.860 --> 00:36:16.230 align:middle line:84%
just intuitively
received information.

00:36:16.230 --> 00:36:19.320 align:middle line:84%
It can be a very
visionary experience.

00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:22.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, I am the first to add--
