00:36:22.200 --> 00:36:24.240 align:middle line:90%
on to add here--

00:36:24.240 --> 00:36:27.990 align:middle line:84%
that the fact that
people report it as real

00:36:27.990 --> 00:36:33.750 align:middle line:84%
