00:36:38.610 --> 00:36:41.640 align:middle line:84%
as a real event from the
scientific perspective

00:36:41.640 --> 00:36:46.170 align:middle line:84%
is that this means that we
have, in fact, recreated

00:36:46.170 --> 00:36:48.320 align:middle line:84%
the experience of
seeing apparitions,

00:36:48.320 --> 00:36:52.230 align:middle line:84%
that this gives us a good
theoretical model, as it were,

00:36:52.230 --> 00:36:54.090 align:middle line:84%
for the experience of
seeing apparitions,

00:36:54.090 --> 00:36:58.860 align:middle line:84%
because that's exactly what
people who see apparitions

00:36:58.860 --> 00:37:01.410 align:middle line:84%
