00:37:08.220 --> 00:37:11.640 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm still somewhat skeptical.

00:37:11.640 --> 00:37:13.450 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what it is.

00:37:13.450 --> 00:37:16.020 align:middle line:84%
I have no doubt there
is something going on.

00:37:16.020 --> 00:37:22.110 align:middle line:84%
I have no doubt that this is
energy from someplace else.

00:37:22.110 --> 00:37:24.819 align:middle line:84%
It may someday turn out to
under-- come to the realization

00:37:24.819 --> 00:37:26.610 align:middle line:84%
that it's some sort of
energy that it comes

00:37:26.610 --> 00:37:30.050 align:middle line:84%
not from the plane where
people are deceased and not

00:37:30.050 --> 00:37:35.070 align:middle line:84%
here, from some other
plane, but without a doubt,

00:37:35.070 --> 00:37:42.310 align:middle line:84%
it does not come from what
