00:37:42.310 --> 00:37:46.340 align:middle line:84%
I know for a fact that
the experiences I've had--

00:37:46.340 --> 00:37:51.610 align:middle line:84%
particularly my
parade of images--

00:37:51.610 --> 00:37:52.960 align:middle line:90%
was not faked.

00:37:52.960 --> 00:37:53.860 align:middle line:90%
It was not.

00:37:53.860 --> 00:37:56.974 align:middle line:90%
It was extremely real.

00:37:56.974 --> 00:37:58.640 align:middle line:84%
There's no way that
could have happened.

00:37:58.640 --> 00:38:00.780 align:middle line:84%
There's no way that
could have been faked.

00:38:00.780 --> 00:38:02.670 align:middle line:90%
I was truly taken aback.

00:38:02.670 --> 00:38:04.980 align:middle line:84%
This was the experience
that I was looking

00:38:04.980 --> 00:38:08.370 align:middle line:84%
for to tell me this
phenomenon was like no other

00:38:08.370 --> 00:38:11.880 align:middle line:84%
that I'd ever had,
and I needed that,

00:38:11.880 --> 00:38:16.830 align:middle line:84%
because although my experiences
on most people's point of view

00:38:16.830 --> 00:38:17.970 align:middle line:90%
would have been--

00:38:17.970 --> 00:38:19.795 align:middle line:90%
meditation and et cetera--

00:38:19.795 --> 00:38:22.170 align:middle line:84%
would have been pretty profound,
it wasn't profound to me

00:38:22.170 --> 00:38:24.780 align:middle line:84%
because I've had
them so many times.

00:38:24.780 --> 00:38:28.140 align:middle line:84%
This was the experience
