00:38:28.140 --> 00:38:29.880 align:middle line:90%
to say no, no, no.

00:38:29.880 --> 00:38:31.780 align:middle line:90%
Something's different here.

00:38:31.780 --> 00:38:34.980 align:middle line:84%
This is not your normal
everyday experience.

00:38:34.980 --> 00:38:36.640 align:middle line:90%
This is exceptional.

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:42.450 align:middle line:84%
So I was just, to use a very
