this is happening.

00:38:54.150 --> 00:38:56.800 align:middle line:90%
This is amazing.

00:38:56.800 --> 00:39:00.760 align:middle line:84%
So to say the least, I
was pretty taken aback.

00:39:00.760 --> 00:39:08.310 align:middle line:84%
And it was very happy,
